<Base
  title="How Many Mailboxes Per Domain for Cold Email? The 2–3 Rule"
  description="Run 2–3 sending mailboxes per cold email domain. Fewer wastes the domain's safe capacity; more concentrates risk and starts looking like bulk infrastructure. The reasoning and the per-domain math."
